headline: U.S. Bancorp: NII Growth, Dividend Increase, Upside
summary: U.S. Bancorp posts strong Q2 earnings with 13% growth, benefits from high interest rates, passes Fed stress test, and offers 4.6% dividend yield. Learn more on USB stock here.
